Problem: tyvars not accepted in top-level type constraint
Code:
    - length : 'a list -> int;
Messages: (compiler messages associated with bug)
    Error: lookTyvar -- unbound tyvar in closed scope
    Error: Impossible error: generalizeTy -- bad arg
    undef list -> int
