Comments:

please put NS32 in $MACHINE case of makeml

maybe:

	NS32)
		if test "$OPSYS" != BSD
		then
			echo "makeml: bad os ($OPSYS) for encore"
			exit 1
		fi
		if test -z "$MO"
		then
			MO="../mo.encore"
		fi
		MODULE="$MODULEKIND"Encore
