Comment: what we need is  %prefer ELSE 0, that is, the ability to give
a hint for the insertion of two tokens in a row.  Right now, %prefer can
only hint about single-token insertions.  This fix has to be done
in mlyacc.
Status: open
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
