  operator domain: ?.t * ?.t
  operand:         ?.t * ?.t
  in expression:
    = (A.x,B.C.A.x)

Comment:
This program is valid, since structure A shares with B.A which shares with B.C.A,
hence A.t and B.C.A.t must be the same (equality) type. However:

